    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/bad74a96fb36ed8b9ac4834bbf6944cb.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/bad74a96fb36ed8b9ac4834bbf6944cb.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>这不是一款自动奔跑或无尽奔跑的游戏。 每个关卡都是手工制作和精心调整的。 您需要控制每一个动作，从冲刺到跳跃，再到不小心被箱子绊倒 :)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/34609ba2d3015a6579b2611f48c80b7a.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/34609ba2d3015a6579b2611f48c80b7a.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>从城市街头，到屋顶高楼，在280个关卡中，您需要仔细规划您的跑酷路线和跑酷动作，克服一切障碍物，尝试以最短的时间和最酷的姿态抵达终点！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/78fba17ef09639643e0bbae9dea6821b.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/78fba17ef09639643e0bbae9dea6821b.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/d7e5d42b111a13bb5433944fd890924d.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/d7e5d42b111a13bb5433944fd890924d.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>这可不是个“有手就能玩”的游戏，至少在您掌握了各种高超技巧之前。真正的跑酷高手总是飞檐走壁，无所不能。您的所有动作都由您自己完全掌控，只有掌握了技巧您才能成功。<br>学习蹬墙跳、滑铲、奔跑攀墙、沿广告牌奔跑、猩猩翻越、控制平衡等动作，通过复杂的动作积累肾上腺素，加速冲刺！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/2b4b3489ff8d805b95aa2416fb06e6fb.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/2b4b3489ff8d805b95aa2416fb06e6fb.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/013038dcab933152d0ee2a1105ad93c1.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/013038dcab933152d0ee2a1105ad93c1.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在关卡中解锁或收集一些外观，打造您的专属装扮。您可以穿得嘻哈，也可以穿得休闲。或许，您还可以Cosplay？<br>您还可以收集众多纪念品，并挑选您最喜欢的一首作为背景音乐。在您的BGM里，没有人可以打败您！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/bab77b4b9747a1f40e5d5121ad14ad99.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/bab77b4b9747a1f40e5d5121ad14ad99.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/518d9e9ad6d2c8b58d741e3edb2a1bb6.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=84 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/518d9e9ad6d2c8b58d741e3edb2a1bb6.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>您的最佳成绩将被记录在排行榜中，供全球玩家瞻仰...或是挑战！<br>您也可以观看任意关卡排行榜上所有玩家的跑酷回放，暂停、减速或者加速。学习他们的技术，提高自己，超越他人！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/5a47731b55dbbc2a0038e80250cf395c.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/5a47731b55dbbc2a0038e80250cf395c.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.mp4?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
